*Nedeljno* se vreme odvija u punom zamahu. (The Sunday weather is in full swing.)

*Nedeljno* popodne bilo je vrlo mirno. (The Sunday afternoon was very quiet.)

*Nedeljno* jutro bilo je obojeno sunčanim zracima. (The Sunday morning was filled with sunshine.)

*Nedeljnim* večerima smo provodili u društvu. (We spent our Sundays in company.)

*Nedeljno* trčanje postalo je naša nova navika. (Sunday running has become our new habit.)